- Mambo!

00:35:36.601 --> 00:35:37.435
Vô!

00:35:46.653 --> 00:35:47.654
Tony!

00:35:49.113 --> 00:35:50.114
Anybodys!

00:35:50.281 --> 00:35:51.366
Cậu đến, tớ vui quá.

00:35:51.533 --> 00:35:54.619
Tony, tớ biết cậu sẽ đến,
cậu bạn. Tớ biết mà.

00:35:54.786 --> 00:35:57.205
